# 03-UI-UX.mdc — User Profiles, Settings & Navigation

**Task:** `2025-12-15__USER-PROFILES`  
**Owner:** UI/UX Agent (proposal only; requires human approval)  
**Status:** Draft  
**Date:** December 15, 2025  

---

## 1. Screen Inventory

| Screen | Route | Access | Purpose |
|--------|-------|--------|---------|
| My Profile | `/profile` | Authenticated | Self-view of user's own profile |
| Other User Profile | `/@[handle]` | Public | Read-only view of another user's profile |
| Edit Profile | `/profile/edit` | Authenticated | Form to update profile fields + avatar |
| Settings | `/settings` | Authenticated | Account settings, privacy, notifications |

