#### Field Display

| Field | Display Rule | Empty State |
|-------|--------------|-------------|
| Avatar | 120px circle, object-fit cover | Default avatar (initials or silhouette) |
| Display Name | H2, primary text color | Username as fallback |
| Handle | Body text, muted, prefixed with @ | Always present (required) |
| Location | Body small, muted, with 📍 icon | Hidden if not set or `showLocation=false` |
| Join Date | Caption, muted, with 📅 icon | "Joined [Month Year]" format |
| Followers/Following | Large number + label below | Show "0" if none |
| Bio | Body text, max 3 lines with "more" expand | Placeholder: "No bio yet" |

#### Actions

| Action | Trigger | Behavior |
|--------|---------|----------|
| Edit Profile | Click "Edit Profile" button | Navigate to `/profile/edit` |
| View Follower list | Click Followers count | Future feature (out of scope) |
| View Following list | Click Following count | Future feature (out of scope) |

