#### Differences from Self-View

| Aspect | Self-View | Other User View |
|--------|-----------|-----------------|
| Primary Action | "Edit Profile" button | "Follow" / "Following" button |
| Private Fields | All visible | Only public fields shown |
| Location | Always shown if set | Only if `showLocation=true` |
| Navigation | Standard nav | Back button to previous page |

#### Public Fields Only

- Avatar
- Display Name
- Handle
- Bio
- Location (if `showLocation=true`)
- Join Date
- Follower/Following counts

**Never shown:** Email, legal name, notification settings, privacy settings.

