#### Field Specifications

| Field | Type | Required | Validation | Editable |
|-------|------|----------|------------|----------|
| Avatar | Image upload | No | JPG, PNG, GIF, WebP; max 5MB | Yes |
| Display Name | Text input | Yes | 1-50 characters | Yes |
| Username/Handle | Text (disabled) | Yes | N/A (read-only) | No |
| Bio | Textarea | No | 0-160 characters | Yes |
| Location | Text input | No | 0-100 characters | Yes |
| Discoverability | Toggle switch | Yes | Boolean | Yes |
| Show Location | Toggle switch | Yes | Boolean | Yes |

#### Avatar Upload Flow

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    AVATAR UPLOAD FLOW                            │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│                                                                 │
│  1. USER CLICKS [Upload Photo]                                  │
│     │                                                           │
│     ▼                                                           │
│  2. FILE PICKER OPENS                                           │
│     - Accept: .jpg, .jpeg, .png, .gif, .webp                   │
│     │                                                           │
│     ▼                                                           │
│  3. CLIENT-SIDE VALIDATION                                      │
│     ├─ File type valid? ──No──▶ Error: "Please upload a JPG,   │
│     │                           PNG, GIF, or WebP image"        │
│     │                                                           │
│     ├─ File size ≤5MB? ──No──▶ Error: "Image must be under 5MB"│
│     │                                                           │
│     ▼                                                           │
│  4. PREVIEW SHOWN                                               │
│     - Show image preview in avatar circle                       │
│     - Show loading spinner during upload                        │
│     │                                                           │
│     ▼                                                           │
│  5. UPLOAD TO STORAGE                                           │
│     ├─ Success ──▶ Avatar updated, show checkmark briefly      │
│     │                                                           │
│     └─ Failure ──▶ Error: "Upload failed. Please try again."   │
│                                                                 │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

#### Avatar Copy Guidelines

| State | Copy |
|-------|------|
| Upload prompt | "Upload Photo" |
| Remove action | "Remove" (only shown if avatar exists) |
| Guidelines note | "Avatars must follow community guidelines and may be reviewed for policy compliance." |
| File type error | "Please upload a JPG, PNG, GIF, or WebP image." |
| File size error | "Image must be under 5MB." |
| Upload in progress | Show spinner, no text change |
| Upload success | Brief checkmark animation, then normal state |
| Upload failure | "Upload failed. Please try again." |
| Remove confirmation | "Remove your profile photo?" with [Cancel] [Remove] buttons |

#### Form Actions

| Action | Location | Behavior |
|--------|----------|----------|
| Back/Cancel | Top-left (mobile) or Cancel button | Discard changes, return to `/profile` |
| Save | Top-right button (primary style) | Validate → Submit → Show feedback |

