## 4. Empty States & Incomplete Profiles

### 4.1 Missing Avatar

```
┌────────────────┐
│                │
│    ┌────┐      │
│    │ SC │      │    ← Initials (first letter of display name or handle)
│    └────┘      │    ← Neutral background (#E5E5E5)
│                │    ← Primary text color for initials
└────────────────┘
```

**Fallback logic:**
1. If display name exists → Use first letter(s) of display name
2. Else → Use first letter of handle

