## 6. Accessibility Requirements

### 6.1 Keyboard Navigation

| Screen | Tab Order |
|--------|-----------|
| My Profile | Edit Profile button → Stats (followers, following) → Bio expand link |
| Other Profile | Follow button → Stats → Bio expand link |
| Edit Profile | Avatar upload → Display name → Bio → Location → Discoverability toggle → Show location toggle → Save button |
| Settings | Account section → Notification toggles → Privacy toggles → Log out → Delete account |

### 6.2 Focus States

All interactive elements must have visible focus indicators:

```css
/* Focus ring specification */
:focus-visible {
  outline: 2px solid var(--accent-primary); /* #FF3366 */
  outline-offset: 2px;
  border-radius: 4px;
}
```

### 6.3 Screen Reader Labels

| Element | aria-label / alt text |
|---------|----------------------|
| Avatar image | "[Display name]'s profile photo" or "Default profile photo" |
| Edit Profile button | "Edit your profile" |
| Follow button | "Follow [display name]" |
| Following button | "Unfollow [display name]" |
| Followers count | "[count] followers" |
| Following count | "Following [count] users" |
| Upload photo button | "Upload profile photo" |
| Remove photo button | "Remove profile photo" |
| Toggle switches | "[Setting name], currently [on/off]" |
| Locked fields | "[Field name], read-only" |

### 6.4 Form Accessibility

| Requirement | Implementation |
|-------------|----------------|
| Labels | All inputs have visible `<label>` elements |
| Required fields | Marked with asterisk (*) and `aria-required="true"` |
| Error states | `aria-invalid="true"` and `aria-describedby` pointing to error message |
| Help text | Associated via `aria-describedby` |
| Character counts | Live region updates: `aria-live="polite"` |

### 6.5 Color Contrast

Per WCAG 2.1 AA (as specified in UI/UX Blueprint):

| Element | Foreground | Background | Ratio |
|---------|------------|------------|-------|
| Primary text | #0A0A0A | #FFFFFF | 21:1 ✓ |
| Secondary text | #737373 | #FFFFFF | 4.84:1 ✓ |
| Muted text | #A3A3A3 | #FFFFFF | 2.68:1 ⚠️ (decorative only) |
| Error text | #EF4444 | #FFFFFF | 4.53:1 ✓ |
| Accent on white | #FF3366 | #FFFFFF | 4.51:1 ✓ |

### 6.6 Motion & Reduced Motion

- All animations respect `prefers-reduced-motion: reduce`
- When reduced motion is preferred:
  - Toast slides → instant appear/disappear
  - Avatar upload spinner → static "Uploading..." text
  - Button press animations → disabled

