│                                              │
│     🏠          👤          ⚙️              │
│    Home      Profile    Settings            │
│   (muted)   (accent)    (muted)             │
│              ● dot                          │
│                                              │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

Active indicator: Dot below icon + accent color on icon and label

### 9.2 Button States

| State | Primary Button | Secondary Button | Danger Button |
|-------|----------------|------------------|---------------|
| Default | `#FF3366` bg, white text | Transparent, border, primary text | Transparent, red text |
| Hover | `#E6295C` bg | Light gray bg | Light red bg |
| Active/Pressed | `#CC2352` bg, scale(0.98) | Darker gray bg | Darker red bg |
| Disabled | `#A3A3A3` bg, muted text | Muted border, muted text | Muted red text |
| Loading | Spinner, disabled | Spinner, disabled | N/A |

### 9.3 Toggle Switch Behavior

```
OFF State                    ON State
┌──────────────────┐        ┌──────────────────┐
│ ○────────────    │   →    │    ────────────● │
│ Gray bg          │        │ Accent bg (#FF3366) │
└──────────────────┘        └──────────────────┘

Transition: 150ms ease-out
```

- Toggles auto-save on change (no explicit save button needed)
- Brief spinner on toggle during save
- Revert to previous state if save fails

### 9.4 Avatar Upload Interaction

```
1. Hover on avatar area (desktop)
