## 13. Out of Scope (Confirmed)

Per 00-TASK-OVERVIEW and 02-ARCHITECTURE-REVIEW:

- Creator-specific profile customization
- Monetization and payout settings
- Admin views and moderation tooling
- Detailed notification preference matrix
- Payment and subscription settings
- Follower/following list pages
- Posts/content tabs on profile (placeholders only)
- Avatar moderation/NSFW detection

